ActNorthwest Territories Act
PrecisAppointment of LEONARD KENNY of Deline, Northwest Territories, to be Deputy Commissioner of Northwest Territories to execute the office and functions of the Commissioner during the absence or illness or other inability of the latter or when the office of the Commissioner is vacant, for a term of three years, effective upon taking and subscribing the oath of office and the oath of allegiance prescribed under section 6 of the Northwest Territories Act.
